<div class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>Your NyumbaSync account has been created by an administrator.</p>
  <p>Click the button below to activate your account and set your password. This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{activationUrl}}" class="button" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #15803d 100%);">Activate My Account</a>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>If the button does not work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <p><a href="{{activationUrl}}">{{activationUrl}}</a></p>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>If you did not request this account, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
  <p>From NyumbaSync team</p>
</div>
